public class SystemInfoMIDlet
extends javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet

SystemInfoMIDlet.java MIDlet can be used to test the System.getProperty API and its implemetation.
This class extends the class javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet. This class is the entry point in the example application. This midlet creates a reference to Infoclass and sets displayable to that class.
